    "We use the dot product of the mapped user embedding and the mapped item embedding to identify the top-𝐾 highest score candidates:𝒔 (𝑓) 𝑖 = Top 𝐾 {F U (𝒆 𝑢 |𝑪 𝑢) ⊤ • 𝒇 𝑖 | ∀𝑢 ∈ U},(7)where F U is the mapping function for the users.",
